title: The Thoughts of Friedrich Nietzsche
itunes:subtitle: Philosophy Now Radio Show #15
itunes:author: Philosophy Now
description: Grant Bartley from Philosophy Now discusses the influence and ideas of Friedrich Nietzsche, the infamous German anti-Christian philosopher, with Ken Gemes, Professor of Philosophy at Birkbeck. First broadcast on 8 November 2011 on Resonance FM.
